OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start, but the cloud
OL,6,Fretreats to the coast through the
OL,7,Fmorning, leaving plenty of sunshine.
OL,8,FTemperatures near average, though
OL,9,Fcooler along the coast with an onshore
OL,10,Fbreeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCoastal low cloud is expected
OL,13,Fto move back inland overnight to
OL,14,Faffect many places, but remaining dry
OL,15,Fwith a light northeasterly breeze.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA cloudy morning for most
OL,18,Fplaces, but low cloud quickly retreats
OL,19,Fto the coast, resulting in a bright
OL,20,Fday for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
